#Learn  about misclassified for each group
#poor self-perceived health
poorind <- which(CLEANDAT$SelfPerceivedHealth == 2,)
poorself <- subset[poorind,]
poorself_clust <- (as.data.frame(subset_clus$clus[,1]))[poorind,]

misspoor <- poorself[CLEANDAT$SelfPerceivedHealth[poorind] != poorself_clust,]
samepoor <- poorself[CLEANDAT$SelfPerceivedHealth[poorind] == poorself_clust,]

summary(colMeans(misspoor) - colMeans(samepoor))
##     Min.  1st Qu.   Median     Mean  3rd Qu.     Max.
